<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>OKKI 看板 — 双轴矩阵</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .subtitle { color: #999; font-size: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  .matrix { display: grid; gap: 1px; background: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
  .cell { background: #fff; padding: 8px; min-height: 60px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; align-content: start; }
  .cell-header { background: #fafafa; padding: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8em; color: #666; text-align: center; }
  .row-label { background: #fafafa; padding: 6px 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.82em; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; }

  .customer-chip { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 14px; font-size: 0.76em; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid transparent; white-space: nowrap; transition: all .12s; }
  .customer-chip:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
  .chip-red { background: #ffebee; border-color: #ffcdd2; color: #b71c1c; }
  .chip-yellow { background: #fff8e1; border-color: #ffecb3; color: #e65100; }
  .chip-grey { background: #f5f5f5; border-color: #eee; color: #888; }

  .chip-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .chip-dot-red { background: #d32f2f; }
  .chip-dot-yellow { background: #f57c00; }
  .chip-dot-grey { background: #bbb; }

  .chip-badge { font-size: 0.7em; padding: 1px 4px; border-radius: 8px; margin-left: 2px; }
  .badge-count { background: rgba(0,0,0,.06); }

  .empty-cell { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #ddd; font-size: 2em; }
  .cold-section { opacity: 0.45; }

  .summary-bar { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 14px; font-size: 0.82em; align-items: center; }
  .summary-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; }
  .legend { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 0.76em; color: #999; align-items: center; }

  .col-cold { background: #fafafa; }
  .stage-header { font-size: 0.78em; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; }
  .stage-count { font-size: 0.7em; font-weight: normal; color: #999; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>OKKI 客户看板</h1>
<p class="subtitle">横轴：客户生命周期 → &nbsp; 纵轴：驱动紧急度 &nbsp; 2026-05-16</p>

